### V9.5 P9 — Blind Structure + Levels E2E flow
###
### 검증 대상:
### - V9.5 P2 (team1): /auth/logout, flat path routing
### - V9.5 P3 (team2): /blind-structures/{bs_id}/levels CRUD (P5 pytest 보강)
### - V9.5 P7 (team2): /skins/deactivate, /users/force-logout, /tables/seats
### - V9.5 P8: drift 0 (BO 135 endpoints, 53 lobby calls, 100% matched)
###
### 사용법: REST Client (VSCode) — 순차 실행. 각 step 의 응답을 다음 step 에서 사용.

@host = http://localhost:8000


### 40.1 Login (POST /auth/logout 검증 사전 준비)
### v0.4.1 D1/D5 정정: username → email, dev seed credentials 사용
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@local",
  "password": "Admin!Local123"
}

> {%
// v0.4.1 D2+D3: response.body.data.accessToken (envelope + camelCase, B-088)
client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}


### 40.2 BlindStructure 생성 (V9.5 정합 — flat path 가정)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "V9.5 E2E Test Structure",
  "levels": [
    {"levelNo": 1, "smallBlind": 100, "bigBlind": 200, "ante": 0, "durationMinutes": 15}
  ]
}

> {%
// v0.4.1 D3: blind_structure_id → blindStructureId (B-088 camelCase 추정)
client.global.set("bs_id", response.body.data.blindStructureId);
%}


### 40.3 Level 추가 (V9.5 P3 신규 endpoint)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures/{{bs_id}}/levels
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "levelNo": 2,
  "smallBlind": 200,
  "bigBlind": 400,
  "ante": 50,
  "durationMinutes": 20
}

> {%
client.global.set("level_id", response.body.data.id);
%}


### 40.4 Level list (V9.5 P3 신규 endpoint)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures/{{bs_id}}/levels
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 40.5 Level 수정 (V9.5 P3 신규 endpoint, partial update)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures/{{bs_id}}/levels/{{level_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "smallBlind": 300,
  "bigBlind": 600
}


### 40.6 Level 삭제 (V9.5 P3 신규 endpoint)
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures/{{bs_id}}/levels/{{level_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 40.7 BlindStructure 정리
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures/{{bs_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 40.8 Logout (V9.5 P2 — POST /auth/logout, DELETE /auth/session 폐기)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### V9.5 cycle 정합 검증:
### - 40.2 Create: BO routing 정합 (PR #85+#86)
### - 40.3-40.6 Levels CRUD: P3+P5 신규 endpoints + pytest
### - 40.8 Logout: P2 SSOT 정합 (DELETE /auth/session → POST /auth/logout)
### - drift audit: 0 unknown (P8 검증 완료, 2026-04-29)
